<pre>



<strong>Fossil Fuel CO<SUB>2</SUB> (Gg) Emissions</strong>
                                             Year
<hr>                  87-88             88-89            89-90           90-91<hr>
CO<SUB>2</SUB> (Gg)         2,543.10          2,906.12         2,620.00        
2,102.00
<hr>


<strong>Greenhouse Gas Emissions From Traditional Fuels 
(Gg)</strong>

