<dt>DOE Carbon Dioxide Information Analysis Center (CDIAC) Home Page	
<dd><a href="http://cdiac.esd.ornl.gov/cdiac">http://cdiac.esd.ornl.gov/cdiac</a>
<dd>(423) 574-0390
<p>
