<html><head>
<title>GCRIO DAAC Information</title>
</head>
<body>
<a href = "http://gcrio.ciesin.org/"><img align = bottom src = "/gifs/gcrio-header.gif"></a>
<hr>
<h2>Distributed Active Archive Centers (DAACs)</h2>
As part of NASA's Mission to Planet Earth/Earth Observing System (MTPE/EOS), nine Distributed Active Archive Centers (DAACs) are responsible for processing, archiving, and distributing MTPE/EOS and related data and information.  Individual DAACs are assigned specific scientific discipline responsibilities.  A full range of user support is available from every DAAC.  

<dl>
<dt><img align=top src="/gifs/ball.yellow.gif">
<a href="http://www.asf.alaska.edu">
Alaska SAR Facility</a>
	<dd><strong>Discipline:</strong>  
	Polar Processes, Synthetic Aperture Radar (SAR) products
<dt><img align=top src="/gifs/ball.yellow.gif">
<a href="http://edcwww.cr.usgs.gov/landdaac/landdaac.html">
Earth Resources Observation Systems (EROS) Data Center</a>
	<dd><strong>Discipline:</strong>
	Land Processes
<dt><img align=top src="/gifs/ball.yellow.gif">
<a href="http://daac.gsfc.nasa.gov">
NASA Goddard Space Flight Center</a>
	<dd><strong>Discipline:</strong>
	Upper atmosphere, global biosphere, atmospheric dynamics, geophysics
<dt><img align=top src="/gifs/ball.yellow.gif">
<a href="http://podaac-www.jpl.nasa.gov">
Jet Propulsion Laboratory</a>
	<dd><strong>Discipline:</strong>
	Physical Oceanography
<dt><img align=top src="/gifs/ball.yellow.gif">
<a href="http://eosdis.larc.nasa.gov">
Langley Research Center</a>
	<dd><strong>Discipline:</strong>
	Radiation budget, tropospheric chemistry, clouds, aerosols
<dt><img align=top src="/gifs/ball.yellow.gif">
<a href="http://wwwdaac.msfc.nasa.gov">
Marshall Space Flight Center</a>
	<dd><strong>Discipline:</strong>
	Hydrologic cycle
<dt><img align=top src="/gifs/ball.yellow.gif">
<a href="http://eosims.colorado.edu:1733">
National Snow and Ice Data Center</a>
	<dd><strong>Discipline:</strong>
	Snow and ice, cryosphere and climate
<dt><img align=top src="/gifs/ball.yellow.gif">
<a href="http://www-eosdis.ornl.gov">
Oak Ridge National Laboratory</a>
	<dd><strong>Discipline:</strong>
	Biogeochemical dynamics
<dt><img align=top src="/gifs/ball.yellow.gif">
<a href="http://sedac.ciesin.org">
Socioeconomic Data and Applications Center</a>
	<dd><strong>Discipline:</strong>
