<DOCHDR>
http://gcrio.org:80/USGCRP/CENR/proguide96/preface.html 198.76.82.10 19970101080946 text/html 5400
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 08:09:20 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
