<P>
While <b>The Executive Advisor</b> intends to offer factual and
up-to-date information on the subjects discussed, this site should
not be regarded as a complete analysis of these subjects.
Professionals should be consulted before implementing any options
presented.<P>

<a href="/FNEA.html">First New England Advisors, Inc.</a> (FNEA) is a
Boston based company 
founded in 1975 which specializes in financial management for a broad
range of clients.  Our tradition of service, professionalism and
teamwork has allowed us to become one of the premiere financial
planning firms in the country.  Our aim is to help you work towards
your financial goals.<P>

This form will enable you to receive more information from our
professional team.  Serious inquiries only, please.<P>
