<HEAD>
<TITLE>Asset Protection</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY background="/grey.gif" text="#000080">
<center><IMG  WIDTH=435 HEIGHT=52 SRC="asset_protection.gif" alt="Asset Protection"></center>
<p>

<dl>
<dt><a href="docs/asset_protection.html"><b>Asset Protection for the
Entrepreneur or Executive</b></a><br>


<dd><a href="summaries/asset_protection.html"><IMG  WIDTH=63 HEIGHT=20 SRC="summary.gif" alt="summary"></a>
<a href="docs/asset_protection.html"><IMG  WIDTH=46 HEIGHT=20 SRC="article.gif" alt="article"></a>
<a href="/consulting.html"><IMG  WIDTH=47 HEIGHT=20 SRC="consult.gif" alt="consult"></a><br>
Entrepreneurs and executives, no matter how successful, are
vulnerable to law suits. As such, measures must be taken to protect
their assets. Two of the most effective tools for accomplishing this
task are the corporate entity and irrevocable trusts.  When used
properly, these powerful tools can protect the assets of the
entrepreneur or executive.<br>


</dl>

