<HEAD>
<TITLE>Insurance Planning</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY background="/grey.gif" text="#000080">
<center><IMG  WIDTH=435 HEIGHT=52 SRC="insurance_planning.gif" alt="Insurance Planning"></center>
<p>

<dl>

<dt><a href="docs/never_leave_workF.html"><b>Disability Income Protection: Never Leave Work Without It</b></a>
<dd><a href="summaries/never_leave_workS.html"><IMG  WIDTH=63 HEIGHT=20 SRC="summary.gif" alt="summary"></a>
<a href="docs/never_leave_workF.html"><IMG  WIDTH=46 HEIGHT=20 SRC="article.gif" alt="article"></a>
<a href="/consult.html"><IMG  WIDTH=47 HEIGHT=20 SRC="consult.gif" alt="consult"></a>
<br>
One out of every three members of the workforce who are now 35 years
old will suffer a long-term disability. The best way to compensate for
a possible future disability is by preparing with disability
insurance. In addition to making up for lost income due to disability,
disability insurance allows individuals to invest and plan correctly,
sure of their future earning power.<P>

<dt><a href="docs/first_to_die_insF.html"><b>When First-To-Die Life
Insurance Is Right For You</b></a>
<dd><a href="summaries/first_to_die_insS.html"><IMG  WIDTH=63 HEIGHT=20 SRC="summary.gif" alt="summary"></a>
<a href="docs/first_to_die_insF.html"><IMG  WIDTH=46 HEIGHT=20 SRC="article.gif" alt="article"></a>
<a href="/consulting.html"><IMG  WIDTH=47 HEIGHT=20 SRC="consult.gif" alt="consult"></a>
<br>First-to-die life insurance has become very popular since its
introduction. It allows insurance for multiple life coverage when only
one death benefit is necessary. First-to-die insurance offers costs
which are 20% - 4O% lower than multiple single life policies. Due to
the savings and practicality of this financial instrument, it is
becoming more widely used in both the business and the home.<P>

</dl>

<p><hr size=4 width=80%>
<center><a href="/cgi-bin/imagemap/navigation"><IMG  WIDTH=359 HEIGHT=63 SRC="/navigation.gif" ISMAP
border=0></a></center>

