<HEAD>
<TITLE>Tax Plannine</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Mark Rosenstein, 23-Oct-1995 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY background="/grey.gif" text="#000080">
<center><IMG  WIDTH=435 HEIGHT=52 SRC="tax_planning.gif" alt="Tax Planning"></center>
<p>

<dl>


<dt><a href="docs/beyond_palmF.html"><b>Beyond the Palm Trees -- Tax Havens and Estate Planning</b></a>
<dd><a href="summaries/beyond_palmS.html"><IMG
 WIDTH=63 HEIGHT=20 SRC="summary.gif" alt="summary"></a>
<a href="docs/beyond_palmF.html"><IMG  WIDTH=46 HEIGHT=20 SRC="article.gif"
alt="article"></a>
<a href="/consulting.html"><IMG  WIDTH=47 HEIGHT=20 SRC="consult.gif" alt="consult"></a><br>

<dd>Offshore trusts are frequently overlooked as vehicles used by
criminals to hide their ill-gotten gains. However, offshore trusts can
be very powerful financial planning tool which can aid in protecting
assets, lowering taxes, and providing deferred earnings.<P>

<dt><a href="docs/strategies_cope_taxF.html"><b>Strategies To Cope With The New Tax Law</b></a>
<dd><a href="summaries/strategies_cope_taxS.html"><IMG
 WIDTH=63 HEIGHT=20 SRC="summary.gif" alt="summary"></a>
<a href="docs/strategies_cope_taxF.html"><IMG  WIDTH=46 HEIGHT=20 SRC="article.gif"
alt="article"></a>
<a href="/consulting.html"><IMG  WIDTH=47 HEIGHT=20 SRC="consult.gif" alt="consult"></a><br>

<dd>The changes in the tax law in 1993 have made many previously
popular tax planning strategies obsolete. It is essential in the field
of financial planning to constantly monitor changes in tax laws, in
order to ensure that an investment is the best possible choice out of
all the choices available.<P>

</dl>

