 WIDTH=63 HEIGHT=20 SRC="/articles/summary.gif" alt="summary"></a>
<a href="/articles/financial_planning.html"><IMG
 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=20 SRC="/articles/abstracts.gif" alt="abstracts"></a><p>
