<TITLE>Links on the net</TITLE> 
<head><body bgcolor=#ffffff  link=#000ac5 vlink=#3a3f61 alink=#747474 text=000000# BACKGROUND="paper.gif"><Basefont size=3>

<img src="logo.gif" hspace=15 vspace=6 align=right ><p>
<br clear=all>
</head><br>

<P>

<img src="redline.gif" vspace=5><p>
<center>
<img src="links.gif" vspace=10 alt=" "><p>
</center>
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT BORDER=0 hspace=10 SRC="net.gif">

Here are some links to other Internet-resources, somewhat related to the ABB World.<br> 
<HR SIZE=2>
<ul><font size=+1>ABB-RELATED RESOURCES</font size=+1><br>
<ul><A HREF="http://www.abb.com"><B>ABB Group</B></A><br>
<A HREF="http://www.abb.fi"><B>ABB Finland</B></A> <br>
<A HREF="http://www.abb.de"><B>ABB Germany</B></A> <br>
