<A HREF="http://www.abb.com/americas/usa/usa.htm"><B>ABB United States</B></A><br>


<HR SIZE=2><P>

<font size=+1>BUSINESS AND INDUSTRY</font size=+1><br>
<ul> <A HREF="http://www.industry.net/"><B>INDUSTRY NET</B></A> a electronic market and newsplace. Free membership.<br>
Index of <A HREF="http://epims1.gsfc.nasa.gov/engineering/ee.html"><B>Electrical Engineering</B></A> and the Virtual library of <A HREF="http://www.ece.iit.edu/~power/power.html"><B> Power Engineering</B></A><br>
Quality references in <a href="http://www.iso.ch/"><b> ISO On-Line</b></a> The Catalogue of all ISO International Standards including drafts, complete lists of members and technical committees, general background of ISO and its structure, facts on the ISO 9000 Forum, and the latest news from ISO. (Officially Mandated)<br>
        
</ul>
<HR SIZE=2><P>

<font size=+1>RESEARCH</font size=+1><br>
<ul>Index to several <A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Economy/Organizations/Public_Interest_Groups/Environment/"><B>Environmental resources</B></A>.<br> <A HREF="http://www.physics.mcgill.ca:80/deptdocs/physics_services.html"><B>Physics around the World</B></A> is a place to find the latest research resources.<br> Index to US <A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Government/Technology_Policy/Information_Technology/National_Information_Infrastructure__US_/"><B>IT structure and concepts</B></A>.<br> 
 Visit the <A HREF="http://www.hike.te.chiba-u.ac.jp/"><B>Ikeda lab of Chiba University</B></A> in Tokyo.<br></ul>
<HR SIZE=2><P>


<font size=+1>OTHER LINKS</font size=+1><br>
