The <A HREF="http://www.sunet.se/sweden/servers.html"><B>Swedish WWW-servers</B></A> list.<br>
Business Magazines and Financial Sources at <A HREF="http://www.enews.com/business.html"><B>Electronic Newsstand</B></A>,  <A HREF="http://www.et.se/afv"><B>Aff&auml;rsv&auml;rlden</B></A> (swedish).<br> 
<A HREF="http://www.ncsa.uiuc.edu/SDG/Software/Mosaic/Docs/whats-new.html"><B>What's New</B></A>, NCSA's updated list on what's new in the WWW-world. Looking for something special, search it through the <A HREF="http://cuiwww.unige.ch/w3catalog"><B>W3 Search Catalouge</B></A>.<br>
Local and <A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Regional_Information/Countries/"><B>Regional information</B></A> resources by country.</ul>
