<TITLE>ABB Power Transmission and Distribution</TITLE>
<head><body bgcolor=#ffffff  link=#000ac5 vlink=#3a3f61 alink=#747474 text=000000# BACKGROUND="paper.gif">
<Basefont size=3>
<img src="logo.gif" vspace=12 hspace=10 align=right >
<br clear=all>
</head><br>
<img src="redline.gif"><p>
<center><img vspace=10 src="Indbuid.gif" alt=""></center><p>


<CENTER><IMG SRC="ABBJPG/INDUSTRY.JPG" HEIGHT=120 alt=""></CENTER>

<BLOCKQUOTE><font size=+0>
Within the industrial part of the segment, ABB manufactures electrical and control equipment, and drying and paint finishing installations for industrial customers.<P>

<A HREF="http://www.abb.se/advant/ocs.htm">Advant OCS</A> the Open Control System for Industrial automation, 
 has become one of ABB's major sales successes. It is used in, for example, the pulp and paper, and the iron and steel industries. Other important products include rotating electrical machines, electromagnetic products for steel mills, drives, high-pressure presses, AC motors and industrial robots. Low-voltage apparatus for industrial and building installations are manufactured here, too, as are also pulp dryers and paint finishing lines for the automotive industry. In addition, ABB's business here includes the installation of electrical equipment and the servicing of ABB's products.<P>

In the building systems part of the segment there are a number of companies active in such areas as air handling equipment, ventilation, building service and refrigeration. ABB supplies air handling systems for public buildings, industries and ships for heating and cooling, humidifying and dehumidifying. The operations also include technical building service and the manufacturing of heat exchangers (coils) and heat meters. Companies in the Refrigeration business area manufacture refrigeration and cooling systems for marine and commercial applications. The food industry is one of the most important customers. 
</font size=+1></BLOCKQUOTE><P>
 
<center>
<table border=3 cellpadding=4 cellspacing=4>
		<tr><td align=left width=140></td>
			<td align=center width=65>ABB Group</td>
			<td align=center width=65>ABB Sweden</td>

		<tr><td align=left width=140>Revenues 1995 MSEK</td>
			<td align=right width=65>106 159</td>
			<td align=right width=65>17 012</td>

		<tr><td align=left width=140>Employees</td>
			<td align=right width=65>89 987</td>
			<td align=right width=65>12 295</td>
</table></center>
