<TITLE>ABB Various Activities</TITLE>
<head><body bgcolor=#ffffff  link=#000ac5 vlink=#3a3f61 alink=#747474 text=000000# BACKGROUND="paper.gif">
<Basefont size=3>
<img src="logo.gif" vspace=12 hspace=10 align=right >
<br clear=all>
</head><br>
<img src="redline.gif"><p>
<center><img vspace=10 src="Various.gif" alt=""></center><p>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="ABBJPG/COMM.JPG" HEIGHT=120 ALT=""></CENTER>

<ul><font size=+0>
ABB's Various Activities include a group of companies active in many different businesses and technology areas.<P>
  
The Swedish ABB, through ABB Asea Skandia, is the largest electrical wholesaler in the Nordic region. Various Activities also include companies manufacturing products and systems in such different areas as, for example, lumber drying and insulating materials, filament-wound products and plastic moulding components, district heating systems, and complete solutions for data communication and telecommunications.<P>
 
There are a number of in-house service companies that meet primarily ABB's own needs. One of these is ABB Infosystems, the Swedish Group's company specializing in information technology. Another similar company is ABB Fastighet, one of Sweden's largest private real estate companies, whose tenants include both ABB companies and other enterprises. 
</font size=+1></ul><P>
 
<center>
<table border=3 cellpadding=4 cellspacing=4>
