<UL>
<P><IMG SRC="Flaktpics/bild2.gif" HEIGHT=128 WIDTH=128 ALIGN=RIGHT><B>ABB
Fl&auml;kt Industri AB</B> has staff of more than 1,000 well-educated specialists.
Our combined expertise in industrial air process technology qualifies us
for mastering the entire chain of supply - from basic research and the
development of processes and products, to marketing, design, production,
installation and start-up.<BR>
Todays company has more than 70 years of experience that make it a world
leader in flue gas cleaning, pulp, paper and board drying and advanced
fans.</P>




The business operations are performed through 5 Divisions: 
<LI>Environmental Systems - Power </LI>

<LI>Environmental Systems - Waste-to Energy &amp; Metallurgy </LI>

<LI>Drying </LI>

<LI>Fans and Production </LI>

<LI>Systems and After-market</LI>

<P> ABB Fl&auml;kt Industri AB is a member of the <A HREF="http://www.abb.se">ABB
Group</A> and operates internationally. <BR>
The vast market resposibility includes among others Sweden, Eastern Europe and
South East Asia.</P>
</UL>

