<title>Welcome to ABB Refrigeration</title>
</head>
<BODY BACKGROUND="paper.jpg" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" TEXT="#000000">
<TABLE  WIDTH=780 HEIGHT=720>
<TR><TD>

<center><img src="logo2.gif" alt="ABB - 2.3 K" width=174 height=66></center> 
<BR><br><br>
<CENTER><img src="welco.gif" alt="WELCOME TO ABB REFRIGERATION AB- 3.6 K" width=598 height=45></CENTER>
<br>
<hr width=90% align=center size=2>

<p><center><b>ABB Refrigeration AB</b> is a Swedish operation
within the worldwide ABB organization.<br>
The main activity of ABB Refrigeration is
the production of innovative and<BR>
technically advanced products for a wide variety of
refrigeration needs.<br>
Customers are primarily companies in the
food and process industries,<BR> 
as well as in shipping.
Over the years, ABB Refrigeration has made<BR> 
itself known in the market with 
equipment and system solutions characterized<br>
by efficient energy utilization, high 
reliability and maximum consideration for<br>
the environment.</P></center>
<hr width=70% align=center size=1>
