<BR CLEAR=ALL>

<H2>Welcome to ABB STAL <BR>
 leaders in steam and gas turbine engineering.</H2>
</CENTER>
<B> ABB Stal is a leading producer of steam and gas turbines for industrial applications. Our products include steam turbine generators, gas turbine power plants, combined cycle and co-generation power plants as well as gas turbines for mechanical drives and ship propulsion. We have been building turbine plants for more than a century with focus on reliability and efficiency. 
ABB Stal is part of the <A HREF="http://www.abb.com"> ABB Group </A>, a world leader in electrical engineering.<BR><BR>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="bar1.gif"><BR></CENTER>


