<H2><A NAME="Plant">Supply of PFBC Plant</A></H2>
ABB Carbon uses the ABB Groups global presence to address the market for Clean Coal  power plants. The ABB Group comprises 1,000 companies in 140 countries. In 1995 the Group had some 210,000 employees and revenues of over US$ 34 billion. <BR><BR>
While ABB Carbon takes on the responsibility for the supply of complete PFBC power plants, this is generally done in partnership wiith other organisations both within and outside of the ABB Group. Examples of appropriate partners are Architect Engineers/Main Contractors, Civil Works Contractors and Plant Construction Companies. 

