<HEAD>
<TITLE>
ABB Flexible Automation - Facts about us
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="bitmaps/bg_grey1.jpg" BGCOLOR="#c0c0c0" VLINK="#0000ff">
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/abb_mt.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT>
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/abbfax30.gif" VSPACE=22>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/ln_red_2.gif"><BR>
<CENTER>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+3>Facts about us</FONT><BR>
</CENTER>
<BR>

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=1 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR>
   <TD WIDTH=149 HEIGHT=152>
     <IMG SRC="bitmaps/hand_mt.gif" WIDTH=147 HEIGHT=150></TD>
   <TD>
     <B>ABB Flexible Automation Headquarters<BR>
     Schaffhauserstrasse 418<BR>
     P.O. Box 8131<BR>
     CH-8050 Z&uuml;rich<BR>
     SWITZERLAND<BR>
     Phone +41-1-318-1092 Fax +41-1-318-1088</B>
</TABLE>
<BR><BR>

<B>
ABB Flexible Automation is the global organization for flexible automation products
and systems ranging from robotics welding and materials handling to paint finishing systems.
A network of Flexible Automation Centers offer local support and expertise in more than 20 countries.<BR> 
</B>
<BR><BR>

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=1 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP>
     <B>President and responsible<BR>
     for the global operations of<BR>
     ABB Flexible Automation:<BR>
     Stelio Demark</B>
   <TD WIDTH=111 HEIGHT=127>
     <IMG SRC="bitmaps/stelio_m.jpg" WIDTH=109 HEIGHT=125><BR>
</TABLE>

<BR>
<B>
Information: <A HREF="mailto:christina.bredin@serop.mail.abb.se">Christina Bredin</A><BR>
</B>
