<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
ABB Flexible Automation - Market offer
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="bitmaps/bg_grey1.jpg" BGCOLOR="#c0c0c0" VLINK="#0000ff">
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/abb_mt.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT>
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/abbfax30.gif" VSPACE=22>
<BR>


<A NAME="robotics_products"></A>
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/ln_red_2.gif"><BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+2>Robotics Products - high quality robots offering the best performance</FONT><BR>
<BR>

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=1 CELLSPACING=1>
<TR>
   <TD WIDTH=77 HEIGHT=77 ROWSPAN=5 VALIGN=TOP><A HREF="prodmain.htm">
       <IMG SRC="bitmaps/irb64_st.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=75 HEIGHT=75></A></TD>
   <TD><IMG SRC="bitmaps/ballblue.gif"></TD>
   <TD><B>Special purpose robots (
     <A HREF="../robotics/product.htm#irb1400">arcwelding</A>,
     <A HREF="../robotics/product.htm#irb6400">spotwelding</A>,
     <A HREF="../flexible/product.htm#irb510">painting</A>)</B></TD></TR>
<TR>
   <TD><IMG SRC="bitmaps/ballblue.gif"></TD>
   <TD><B><A HREF="../flexible/product.htm#irb8000">Gantry robots</A></B></TD></TR>
<TR>
   <TD><IMG SRC="bitmaps/ballblue.gif"></TD>
   <TD><B><A HREF="../robotics/product.htm#control">Robot controllers</A></B></TD></TR>
<TR>
   <TD><IMG SRC="bitmaps/ballblue.gif"></TD>
   <TD><B><A HREF="../robotics/product.htm#robware">Software products</A></B></TD></TR>
<TR>
   <TD><IMG SRC="bitmaps/ballblue.gif"></TD>
   <TD><B>Accessory products</B></TD></TR>
</TABLE>
<BR>

An installed base of 50,000 robots reflects 20 years experience of robot based automation.
Arm type robots are manufactured in <A HREF="../robotics/welcome.htm">Sweden</A>,
and <A HREF="flexlist.htm#norway">Norway</A>,
gantry robots in <A HREF="flexlist.htm#switzerland">Switzerland</A>. At these Supplying
Units we have in-house expertise in both robot controller and robot arm development. Over 200 engineers
work in R&D to ensure continuous development of arm configurations and mechanical structures, motors
and gears; motion control, robot programming and operator interface.
<BR><BR><BR>


<A NAME="robotics_systems"></A>
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/ln_red_2.gif"><BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+2>Robotics Systems</FONT><BR> 
<BR>

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=1 CELLSPACING=1>
<TR>
   <TD WIDTH=77 HEIGHT=77><A HREF="../robotics/applic.htm">
       <IMG SRC="bitmaps/apaw_s.jpg" BORDER=0 WIDTH=75 HEIGHT=75></A></TD>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP>
Cost efficient robot-based systems that cover the process of automotive manufacture
and its suppliers - from press shop, body shop and paint shop to trim and final assembly.<BR> 
For industrial and consumer goods markets <A HREF="../robotics/applic.htm"> typical applications</A>
are packaging, palletizing, machine tending, materials handling, deburring, cutting,
arc welding and assembly.</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
<BR>

<B>Centers of Excellence</B> which house expertise in design, engineering,
project management and systems capability:<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=1 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR>
   <TD><IMG SRC="bitmaps/balloran.gif"></TD>
   <TD>Body-in-White</TD>
   <TD><A HREF="flexlist.htm#france">ABB Prciflex Systems s.n.c.</A></TD>
   <TD>Beauchamp, France</TD></TR>
<TR>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP><IMG SRC="bitmaps/balloran.gif"></TD>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP>Engine &<BR>Transmission</TD>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP><A HREF="flexlist.htm#germany">ABB Flexible Automation GmbH</A></TD>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP>Langenfeld, Germany</TD></TR>
<TR>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP><IMG SRC="bitmaps/balloran.gif"></TD>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP>Arc Welding</TD>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP><A HREF="flexlist.htm#sweden">ABB Welding Systems</A><BR>
      <A HREF="flexlist.htm#usa">ABB Flexible Automation Inc.</A></TD>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP>Lax&aring;, Sweden<BR>
       Fort Collins CO, USA</TD></TR>
<TR>
   <TD><IMG SRC="bitmaps/balloran.gif"></TD>
   <TD>Packaging</TD>
   <TD><A HREF="flexlist.htm#france">ABB Flexible Automation s.n.c.</A></TD>
   <TD>Troyes, France</TD></TR>
