   <TD><IMG SRC="bitmaps/balloran.gif"></TD>
   <TD>Waterjet cutting</TD>
   <TD><A HREF="flexlist.htm#sweden">ABB I-R Robotized Waterjet AB</A></TD>
   <TD>Ronneby, Sweden</TD></TR>
