<p><hr width=400><p>
<center>
<TABLE WIDTH=450 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=7 CELLSPACING=1>

  <TR>

    <TD valign=top align=right>ABB Fl&auml;kt Industri has a center for research and development in the Air Pollution Control, Drying and Industrial fan fields. Some 80 engineers and scientists are stationed at the center. They are supported by facilities that range from laboratories to full-scale or large-scale test facilities.<br>
The center has worldwide responsibility for product and system development within the mentioned fields.</TD>
		<TD><IMG SRC="Flaktpics/rd.jpg" border=1><p></TD>

  </TR>

  
</TABLE>

