<head>
<title>ABB Refrigeration</TITLE>
</head>
<body BACKGROUND="paper.jpg" bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000">
<TABLE WIDTH=780 HEIGHT=1300>
<TR><TD>

<img src="logo.gif" alt="ABB - 1.1 K" width=115 height=45 align=right hspace=20>
<br><br><br>
<hr width=90% align=center size=1>
</head>
<center><h3><b>ABB Refrigeration AB<br>
-development and manufacture of<br>
advanced refrigeration products</b></h3></center>
<hr width=60% align=center size=1>
<BR>


<img src="STAL1.jpg" alt="COMPRESSOR - 15.5 K" width=320 height=210 border=2 align=left>

<center><b>ABB Refrigeration AB</b> develops and produces
the majority of the key products for ABB's international contracting operation
in industrial and marine refrigeration.
The main products are screw compressors with
associated units, liquid chillers and valves, 
all of which are designed to comply with several  
leading standards, norms and classification 
requirements. 
The operation economy and reliability of these 
products are enhanced by a microprocessor based 
control and regulating system using in-house  
developed software. 
Operations at ABB Refrigeration also include a   
research and development unit covering ABB's
needs in refrigeration products.
In addition the organization comprises a department for plant 
engineering and training
center for internal <BR>as well 
as customers personnel.
</center>
<br>
<hr width=90% align=center size=1>

<br><br>

<h3><b><center>ABB Stal Marine<br> - a leading supplier <br>
     of marine refrigeration</b></h3>
<hr width=55% size=1>

<p><b>ABB Stal Marine</b> is responsible for system 
design, sales, installation and service of  
refrigeration<BR> installations on board ships, 
throughout the world. 
Operations and products cover a wide spectrum 
of the <BR>refrigeration needs in different types 
of vessels, including cargo and provisions 
refrigeration and comfort<BR> cooling.   
ABB Stal Marine is among the world's leading 
company's in marine refrigeration, with large<BR> 
market shares in applications for reefers, 
container ships, passenger and cruise liners.<br></p> 

<hr width=80% align=center size=1>

<br><br>

<p><b><h3>ABB Stal-Litzell <br>- refrigeration for<br>
Swedish industry and trade</h3></b></p>

<hr width=50% align=center size=1>

<br>

<img src="screw.jpg" alt="COMPRESSOR SCREW UNDER CONSTRUCTION - 34.8 K" width=480 height=224 border=1 align=right>

<b>ABB Stal-Litzell</b> is Sweden's largest <BR>supplier 
of refrigeration equipment for a wide range of applications. 
Customers represent many branches of industry  
and trade. Food processing industry and supermarkets
represents important customer categories
The company also has extensive  
operations in the area for air conditioning. 
A nationwide service organization is available  
to customers for regular maintenance and   
upgrading of their refrigeration installations   
- important factors<BR> for operating economy and  
profitable investments.&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp  &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp  &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp
&nbsp<br><br></center>
<hr width=80%size=3>
<a href="welcome.html"><h3>Back to main menu.</h3></a>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
</html>
