<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>We care for the environment.</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<body BACKGROUND="paper.jpg" bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000">
<TABLE WIDTH=775 HEIGHT=1000>
<TR><TD>
<img src="logo.gif" alt="ABB - 1.1 K" width=115 height=45 align=right hspace=20>
<br><br><br>
<hr width=90% align=center>
<br><br>
<img src="environ.gif" alt="CARING FORE THE ENVIRONMENT - 3.3 K" width=197 height=125 align=left>
<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>

<img src="sky2.jpg" alt="SKY - 5.2 K" width=222 height=188 hspace=10 vspace=10 border=1 align=right>
<BR>
<center><p>We have a sincere
commitment to environmental questions. For
a long time, the majority of our refrigeration
installations have used ammonia as refrigerant 
and this technique is now being introduced
in comparatively small installations.
Ammonia is at present the only medium
without a negative effect on either 
the ozone layer or global warming.
  We are heavily engaged in testing future
alternatives to the hazardous chlorinated
refrigerants.
  At the same time, we pay attention to 
environmental aspects such as gas tightness
and efficient energy utilization, right from the
system and component design stage.
  We take a great interest in all aspects that
have a direct impact on the human environment.<br></center>
<BR><BR>
<hr width=80% align=center size=1>
<br>
<p><center><font size=+1><b>COMFORT COOLING</b></font></center>
<br>
<hr width=90% align=center size=1>
<center>Cooling equipment for air conditioning
systems plays an important part in people's
well-being and performance. <BR>We supply
cooling installations in industrial, public and
private environments. Our extensive chiller
ranges cover <BR>most requirements and include
a new type which uses a very small charge of
ammonia refrigerant.
  Here too, <BR>our know-how in environment friendly 
refrigerants and automatic control
systems is a vital resource.<br></center>
<br>
<hr width=80% align=center size=1>
<br>
<p><center><font size=+1><b>HEAT UTILIZATION</b></font></center>
<br>
<hr width=80% align=center size=1>
<br>
<center>Both industrial and sports facilities are
making increased use of the heat normally
generated by refrigeration systems.<BR>
  In addition to straightforward heat recovery,
 we offer an extensive product programme
and know-how in heat pumps.<BR> These can be
integrated with advantage in our installations
for producing heat that can be used in buildings 
<BR>and processes, as well as for tap water.
The benefits are both economic and environmental.<br>
</center>
<br>
<hr width=80% align=center size=6>
<a href="welcome.html"><h3>Back to main menu.</h3></a>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
