<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>ABB STAL PRODUCT OVERVIEW</TITLE>
</HEAD>


<BODY BACKGROUND="tile.gif">

<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="logo2.gif" ALT="ABB"><BR>
<IMG SRC="abbname2.gif" ALT="ABB STAL" WIDTH=151 HEIGHT=38 ALIGN=absbottom>
<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<IMG SRC="bar1.gif" WIDTH=600 HEIGHT=2>
<BR clear=all>
<FONT  SIZE=+2><STRONG>P<FONT SIZE=-1>RODUCT INFORMATION</FONT></STRONG></FONT><BR><BR>
<B><FONT SIZE=+2>ABB Stal</FONT> specialises in industrial turbine technology. The company supplies steam and gas turbine products in the medium output range for power and heat generation
as well as mechanical drives including marine propulsion. <BR><BR>
ABB Stal is the ideal partner for <A HREF="combined.htm">combined cycle</A> and cogeneration plants. The fact that we manufacture the prime components ourselves is one of the reasons for the proven high performance of all our plants.
</B>


<BR><BR CLEAR=ALL>
<BR><TABLE CELLPADDING=2 CELLSPACING=2>
<TR><TD><IMG SRC="hpassy.gif" ALT="High-pressure steam turbine assembly" WIDTH=108 HEIGHT=88 ALIGN=top></TD><TD><FONT  SIZE=+2><STRONG><A NAME="steam turbines">ATP steam turbines - compact and flexible</A><BR></STRONG></FONT><B><FONT  SIZE=-1>ABBs industrial steam turbine programme, the Advanced Turbine Program, ATP, includes four turbine types for condensing as well as back-pressure applications. The ATP turbines feature modular build-up for maximum flexibility and are built from proven components. Extensive factory assembly ensures total quality
and reduces installation time. </FONT></B></TD></TR>

<TR><TD><FONT  SIZE=-1><I>High-pressure steam turbine assembly</TD><TD></TD></TR>
<TR><TD><FONT  SIZE=-1><a href="hpassyhr.gif">(Load image 117 kB)<BR><BR></A></I></TD><TD></TD></TR>

