<BR><BR>
<H3>Power plant service</H3>
<P><STRONG>ABB Stal has long experience of servicing large steam turbines in nuclear and fossil-fired power plants.

We specialise in overhauling turbines, condensers, reheaters, heat exchangers and valves with servo motors with a minimum of outage time. Our technical specialists are available for consulting services, inspection and other qualified tasks. We also offer turbine retrofitting for more power as well as modernisation of control systems. </STRONG>
<BR><H4>For further information about ABB STAL power plant service, please contact:</H4>
<ADRESS>Bengt Assarsson<BR>
telephone +46 122 81063 (direct)<BR>
fax + 46 122 195 93<BR>
