<P>
<h3>Power plant rehabilitation</h3>
<p><strong>Rehabilitation and upgrading are effective means to get additional output, better availability and improved environmental performance from old deteriorated power plants. <P>

ABB Stal has wide experience from modernisation of power plant equipment including steam turbines, condensers, generators, controls and electrical equipment. </strong>
<br><h4>For further information about ABB STAL power plant rehabilitation, please contact:</h4>
