<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
ABB Flexible Automation in Sweden
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="bitmaps/bg_grey1.jpg" BGCOLOR="#c0c0c0" VLINK="#0000ff">
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/abb_mt.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT>
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/abbfax30.gif" VSPACE=22>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="bitmaps/ln_red_2.gif"><BR>
<CENTER>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+3>Facts about Flexible Automation in Sweden</FONT><BR>
</CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=1 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR>
   <TD WIDTH=77 HEIGHT=77>
     <IMG SRC="bitmaps/gregb_st.gif" WIDTH=75 HEIGHT=75></TD>
   <TD VALIGN=TOP>
     <B>ABB Flexible Automation AB<BR>
     Terminalv&auml;gen<BR>
     S-721 75 Vsters<BR>
     SWEDEN<BR>
     Phone +46-21-344-500 Fax +46-21-125-497</B><BR>
</TABLE>
<BR>

<B>
ABB Flexible Automation AB konstruerar och levererar robotanlggningar i Sverige fr <NOBR>bl a</NOBR> svetsning,
lackering, materialhantering, maskinbetjning, bearbetning, och montering. 
<BLOCKQUOTE>
