<P>
With a team of experienced analysts, the Power Systems Analysis Department
undertakes <A HREF="h06.htm"> analytical services</A> to support systems
and project engineering of ABB companies worldwide. The services are also
available to other companies such as electrical utilities, consultants,
industries, etc.
<P>
