<HTML>
<HEAD>
  <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
  <META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="ABB Power Systems AB">
  <TITLE>ABB HVDC projects - Leyte-Luzon</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="paper.jpg">
<P>
<A NAME="DDE_LINK2"><IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 HEIGHT=30 SRC="abblog5.gif"
    alt=""> <IMG SRC="powlog1.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></A>
<P>
<IMG width=100% SRC="redline.gif" alt=" ">
<H2>
  Leyte - Luzon HVDC Power Transmission Project
</H2>
<P>
<TABLE CELLPADDING="2">
  <TR>
    <TD ROWSPAN=2>
      <IMG SRC="leytemap.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
    </TD>
    <TD>
    </TD>
  </TR>
  <TR>
    <TD VALIGN="Bottom">
      <A HREF="l1392.htm"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="leyte2.jpg" ALT="Photos" WIDTH="61"
	  HEIGHT="50"></A>
    </TD>
  </TR>
</TABLE>
<P>
<H4>
  National Power Corporation is constructing a 440 MW, 350 kV monopolar HVDC
  link to transfer power from the geothermal power plant on the island of Leyte,
  to the southern part of the main island of Luzon to feed the existing AC
  grid in the Manila region.
</H4>
<H4>
  Contract comprising design, delivery, installation and commissioning of two
  converter stations as well as electrode and cable stations was awarded in
  1994 to ABB Power Systems AB, Sweden in cooperation with Marubeni Corporation,
  Japan
</H4>
<H4>
  The new HVDC interconnection will be beneficial both to industry and the
  inhabitants of the Manila area, not only through the added power influx,
  but also through the inherent stabilizing effect of an HVDC link on the AC
  network.
</H4>
<H4>
  The use of geothermal power contributes significantly to environmental
  improvements on a national as well as a global scale.
</H4>
<P>
<H3>
  Project status December 1996
</H3>
<H4>
  System engineering and equipment design have been compleeted and transportation
  to the sites in the Philippines is in progress.
</H4>
<H4>
  The civil construction at the sites is proceeding well and installation will
  start in January 1997.
</H4>
<P>
<H4>
  Technical Data:
</H4>
<P>
<TABLE border>
  <TR>
    <TD>
      Commissioning year:
    </TD>
    <TD>
      1997
    </TD>
  </TR>
  <TR>
    <TD>
      Power Rating:
    </TD>
    <TD>
      440 MW
    </TD>
  </TR>
  <TR>
    <TD>
      DC Voltage:
    </TD>
    <TD>
      350 kV
    </TD>
  </TR>
  <TR>
    <TD>
      Length of overhead line:
    </TD>
    <TD>
      420 km
    </TD>
  </TR>
  <TR>
    <TD>
      Length of submarine cable:
    </TD>
    <TD>
      23 km
    </TD>
  </TR>
</TABLE>
<P>
  <HR>
<P>
<CENTER>
  <IMG SRC="abbhand.gif" ALIGN=TOP> | <A HREF="home.htm">ABB Power Systems
  Home Page</A> | <A HREF="http://www.abb.se">ABB Sweden</A> |
</CENTER>
