<HEAD><TITLE>Design Reconstitution</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="headabba.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5><TR>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=CENTER><FONT SIZE=5><B>Design Reconstitution</B></FONT></TD>
</TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=0><TR>
<TD><IMG SRC="b06im1.gif"></TD>
</TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<BR>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0><TR>
<TD WIDTH=412>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=0 ALIGN=Right><TR>
<TD><IMG SRC="b06im2.gif"></TD>
</TR></TABLE>
Together with the plant operators, ABB Atom is carrying out design reconstitution projects to re-evaluate the design and safety status of the ABB Atom BWRs that have been operating for 15 years or more.
<P>
The performance and safety of the plants are compared to present-day requirements and to design characteristics of modern plants in a second phase of the design reconstitutions. The results of these comparisons provide an excellent basis for additional plant modernizations.
<P>
Another major benefit of the design reconstitution projects is their contribution to the transfer of knowledge between organizations and between experienced and less experienced personnel.
<P>
The design reconstitution projects started in 1993 and will be finished in 1998.</TD>
</TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="linerbow.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0><TR> 
