<HEAD><TITLE>ERFATOM</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="headabba.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5><TR>
<TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=CENTER><FONT SIZE=5><B>ERFATOM</B></FONT></TD>
</TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=0><TR>
<TD><IMG SRC="b11im1.gif"></TD>
</TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<BR>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0><TR>
<TD WIDTH=407>
ERFATOM is the Nordic utilities&#146; common organization for the exchange of experience. Occurrences, events, and other circumstances involving nuclear power are analyzed and evaluated as to their relevance for the boiling water reactors of the utilities. Fast and direct communication assures that all experience essential to safety reach those plants that might be concerned.
<P>
In order to benefit most from the knowledge and experience of the plant designer, the activities are located in the offices of ABB Atom in V&auml;ster&aring;s, Sweden. The project is manned by the members of ERFATOM.
<P>
ABB Atom offers administrative support and project management. The work is headed by a steering committee with representatives from the utilities.
</TD>
</TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="linerbow.gif"></CENTER>
