<TD WIDTH=407>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=0 ALIGN=Right><TR>
<TD><IMG SRC="b18im2.gif"></TD>
</TR></TABLE>
Service of process components means that ABB Atom can give all the support and service necessary for the various components requested by our customers.
<P>
ABB Atom has gathered comprehensive knowledge of and experience from components through construction and continuous service in nuclear power plants. We use our know-how in assignments such as
<P>
&#128;	specifying and selecting new components procurement and delivery of components and spare parts,
<P>
&#128;	analysis regarding new demands and influence of test results on existing components,
<P>
&#128;	troubleshooting,
<P>
&#128;	performing service and carrying out maintenance on components,
<P>
&#128;	long-term and environmental tests of components,
<P>
&#128;	producing test and maintenance instructions.
<P>
ABB Atom has rigs for functional and material testing as well as mobile equipment for on-site component and material tests.</TD>
