<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>ABB Network Partner - the Company 2</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY  BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#FF0A11" VLINK="#930000">
<IMG ALIGN=Right SRC="logo.gif" WIDTH=116 HEIGHT=55 BORDER=0>

<TABLE CELLSPACING=1 CELLPADDING=0 BORDER=0>
<TR valign=top>
	<TD  height=100 WIDTH=180>
<A HREF="senete.html"><IMG SRC="netbut.JPG" WIDTH=120 HEIGHT=15 border=0></A><p>

</TD>
<TD WIDTH=500 colspan=2>&nbsp;</TD>

<TR VALIGN=TOP>
	<TD WIDTH=140></TD>
<td WIDTH=400 HEIGHT=40 colspan=2></td>

<TR VALIGN=TOP>
		<TD WIDTH=180 valign=top><IMG SRC="solution.JPG" WIDTH=180 HEIGHT=115 BORDER=0><p>
<I>The Complete<BR>
Solution</I></TD>

<td WIDTH=400 COLSPAN=3><P>
<FONT SIZE=+3>The Complete Solution</FONT><P>

ABB Network Partner AB in Vsters, Sweden, is a complete supplier of integrated information systems for the power industry. We offer solutions for the power system monitoring, control and protection as well as the business management.<P>


<B>A total system concept</B><BR>
With the Panorama concept we offer systems and products for IT-solutions for the entire power process. From the power producer to the end-consumer. Panorama includes everything from independent products to total integrated solutions, also with a turn-key commitment.

<DD>Panorama is known for its modular thinking and openness. Everything works in integration modes as well as in stand-alone operations. This means we can always develop the right solution to fit the application.<P>


<B>A complete set of products and systems</B><BR>
Our IT-solutions include systems for information support of business management within the power industry. S.P.I.D.E.R. BMS provides full control over business routines and the commercial flow. Your customer service will be faster and the information more reliable. As a result, your company will be more competitive.

<DD>S.P.I.D.E.R. EMS is Panorama's system for energy management and security analysis in power systems. Not only will it improve your economy but by optimizing of the power system's operations you'll be able to supply electricity as promised thanks to proper analysis reducing the number of serious interruptions. Follow-up and reports will add to the experience within your organization.

<DD>S.P.I.D.E.R. DMS offers advanced distribution network modeling. Operations monitoring improves, work routines become more secure and information to the customer increases. Integration with other systems provides information throughout the entire organization, in the office as well as in the field.

<DD>S.P.I.D.E.R. SCADA, S.P.I.D.E.R. Compact and S.P.I.D.E.R. MicroSCADA are used for the basic monitoring and control of power systems as well as other industry processes e.g. district heating networks and distribution networks for oil and gas.

<DD>PYRAMID is the market's most advanced system for the coordinated automation of substations, transformers and generators. We offer integrated solutions for all voltage levels. The intelligent PYRAMID terminals contain unique protection algorithms for reliable fault disconnection and detailed fault diagnosis. Added to that are automatic control functions, status monitoring, disturbance recording, remote setting of parameters as well as control center adaptation. In short, the PYRAMID system offers the customer total integration with the lowest life-cycle cost.


<DD>Our modern COMBIFLEX program is the market's most complete system for building relay equipment even in the harshest of environments. It combines easy construction with the highest operation reliability. New, state-of-the-art products are constantly being introduced for use in existing facilities and for new constructions as well. This means our COMBIFLEX customers can receive the lowest maintenance costs during the life of the installation.

<DD>S.P.I.D.E.R. DSM provides for automatic meter reading in deregulated and privatized electricity markets. It also encompasses load management concepts. Two-way communication makes it possible to increase customer service and cut peak loads.

<DD>Panorama's Alpha-technique offers a new dimension in energy metering through its many built-in functions. As part of an integrated customer communication system, the information exchange for an open power market will increase in speed and accuracy. Customer's quality of service will be enhanced.

<DD>FoxNet is Panorama's fiber optic system for advanced communication solutions. It allows maximum transfer speed with a multitude of flexible network configurations. A tried and true power line carrier system for high and low voltages is included. Flexibility provides the opportunity to create the proper solution to fit the need.<P>


<B>Our total responsibility</B><BR>
We assume full responsibility. We can deliver complete solutions including design, application development, installation and project management. Or we can deliver stand-alone products. All adapted to meet the need.

<DD>In addition, we can help with investment and benefit evaluations in order to better design system solutions. We can help in the training of personnel and we have the resources for maintenance and system upgrades.<P>
In short, we're a partner in every sense of the word.
<P>&nbsp;<P></td>


