<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>ABB Network Partner - Panorama</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY  BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#FF0A11" VLINK="#930000">
<IMG ALIGN=Right SRC="logo.gif" WIDTH=116 HEIGHT=55 BORDER=0>

<TABLE CELLSPACING=1 CELLPADDING=0 BORDER=0>
<TR valign=top>
	<TD  height=100 WIDTH=180>
<A HREF="senete.html"><IMG SRC="netbut.JPG" WIDTH=120 HEIGHT=15 border=0></A><p>

</TD>
<TD WIDTH=500 colspan=2>&nbsp;</TD>

<TR VALIGN=TOP>
	<TD WIDTH=140></TD>
<td WIDTH=400 HEIGHT=40 colspan=2></td>

<TR VALIGN=TOP>
		<TD WIDTH=180 valign=top><IMG SRC="promise.JPG" WIDTH=180 HEIGHT=115 BORDER=0><P>
<A HREF="netpan01.html"><IMG SRC="panbut.JPG" WIDTH=120 HEIGHT=15 BORDER=0></A>
</TD>

<td WIDTH=400 COLSPAN=3>
<FONT SIZE=+3>Panorama is complete</FONT><P>

Panorama establishes integrated computing for the entire power company. Different information technology solutions can interoperate -  for management support and business functions as well as engineering, planning and operation.
<DD>Panorama offers harmonized operation between control centers, protection terminals, local control as well as metering systems. 
<DD>It spans a wide scope of applications from meter algorithms, line and busbar protection to load forecasts, security analysis, optimal power flows and training simulators. It includes services for your business management: trouble call entries, work order management, energy trading, metering, and so on. 
<DD>And the power system communications that ties it all together.<P>

<B>The business tool for competition</B><BR>
Panorama's business management system - S.P.I.D.E.R. BMS - supports your business routines and makes you more competitive. Your customer service will be improved by faster and more accurate information; from real-time processing to commercial transactions. Contract handling and trading of power and energy are facilitated. Customer databases can be built. Accounting and billing can be more effective. <P>

<B>Optimize the use of generation</B><BR>
<B>and transmission assets</B><BR>

Panorama's energy management system - S.P.I.D.E.R. EMS -  offers a full range of advanced applications. They analyze, optimize  and control operation conditions while maintaining system security. S.P.I.D.E.R. EMS  installations range from standardized to large integrated 
systems. S.P.I.D.E.R. EMS also offers its applications software in stand-alone solutions.<P>

<B>Customer satisfaction at the lowest cost</B><BR>

Panorama's distribution management system - S.P.I.D.E.R. DMS - supports all activities in a distribution company, encompassing modeling of the network with interfaces to automated mapping and facilities management. 
<DD>S.P.I.D.E.R. DMS installations range from small, dedicated systems to large company-wide ones, integrating all work procedures; in the control room, in the office and in the field.<P>

<B>For secure network operation</B><BR>
Panorama's supervisory control system - S.P.I.D.E.R. SCADA and MicroSCADA  - establishes the open platform on which is built versatile data acquisition and control functionality combined with efficient and secure database management. With real-time performance. Its user interface offers full graphics technology with multimedia features. It ranges from compact, standardized systems to large and tailor-made ones. Supporting both energy management and distribution automation.<P>

<B>Lowest life-cycle cost for 
your substation</B>
Panorama's substation automation system - PYRAMID SAS - provides for integrated solutions on all voltage levels. It includes a full set of applications, from distributed data acquisition and control to full-graphics presentation. It provides for disturbance recording and remote settings of protection terminals. PYRAMID SAS ranges from small, remote terminal units to large, distributed control systems. <P>

<B>Maximize power network 
availability</B><BR>
Panorama offers a complete protection and control system - PYRAMID Intelligent Protection - that includes protection terminals for generation as well as for all parts of your 
network. PYRAMID's reliable and novel protection algorithms are based on ABB's world-wide experience. The set of protections can operate in a stand-alone fashion as well as fully integrated.<P>

<B>Savings by managing peak loads</B><BR>
Panorama - S.P.I.D.E.R. DSM and LMS - improves your demand-side management. Whether you prefer direct load control or want to develop indirect strategies. Its centralized load control and real-time pricing can help to reduce peak loads or smooth consumption profiles. S.P.I.D.E.R. DSM and LMS offers reliable communication all the way to your customer.<P>

<B>The business link to 
your customer</B><BR>
Panorama's Alpha technology provides innovative metering packaged to meet market demands. It has multi-functional capabilities that go beyond the traditional scope, both for metering and control. Alpha-meters may be integrated into centralized as well as local demand-side systems, e.g. for automatic meter reading or home automation.<P>

<B>The solution for power system communications</B><BR>
Panorama's FoxNet fiberoptic systems provide maximum capacity and ensure high interference immunity. Panorama also includes power-line carrier systems  for long distance transmission and distribution networks. The result: flexible and effective communication for power company needs.
And our communication solutions meet additional needs -  in partnership with e.g. microwave or satellite communication suppliers.</td>

<TR VALIGN=TOP>
	<TD WIDTH=140><A HREF="netpan04.html"><IMG SRC="next.JPG" WIDTH=120 HEIGHT=15 BORDER=0></A><P>
<A HREF="senete.html"><IMG SRC="front.JPG" WIDTH=120 HEIGHT=15 BORDER=0></A></TD>
