<TR VALIGN=TOP>
		<TD WIDTH=180 valign=top><IMG SRC="future.JPG" WIDTH=180 HEIGHT=115 BORDER=0><P>
<A HREF="netpan01.html"><IMG SRC="panbut.JPG" WIDTH=120 HEIGHT=15 BORDER=0></A>
</TD>

<td WIDTH=400 COLSPAN=3>
<FONT SIZE=+3>Panorama - a highway to the future</FONT><P>

The Panorama concept is here to stay. A network management system can no longer be seen from just a life-cycle perspective where you invest once and then write off your investment over a long period of time. 
<DD>It must be looked upon as an ongoing process where continuous upgrades and product and system adaptations meet the ever-changing requirements of a competitive electricity market. Costs must always be relevant to quantified benefits of your functionality. 
<DD>Let us show you how Panorama  can give you a satisfactory pay-off for your investment. <P>

<B>Technical leadership in R&D</B><BR>
All our efforts in R&D are targeted for completeness, continuity and compatibility. Each and every year we spend more on R&D than anyone else in our business. This underlines our commitment to remain the industry leader. Today and tomorrow.
<DD>Product development is targeted for technical leadership. This is a long-term program aimed at top quality. We conform to standards and offer migration paths through compatibility. Everything we do is based on open platforms. That offers scalability for easy expansion and makes integration with other systems easy. It provides connectivity for a multi-vendor environment and portability for migration to new technologies.
<DD>Our software is designed for utilities in the midst of a rapidly changing market. They're all based on a versatile kernel for supervisory control. We have a complete set of application programs. In Panorama, modularization is key to distributed processing.<P>

<B>Designed for a changing world</B><BR>
All products and systems within Panorama are designed to be adaptable to market development. Regardless of which way it goes.
<DD>They have built-in tools for operation, engineering and maintenance. They have a flexible architecture for fine tuning to meet performance and availability requirements. There are redundancy schemes and portability for hardware platforms. Naturally, these platforms are continuously upgraded.
<DD> All our products and systems are designed according to leading technology and are based on international standards and targeted for the lowest possible cost.<P>

<B>Open to the future</B><BR>
Adopt the Panorama concept and you're on a safe route to the future. Whatever you buy today, you can be sure it will fit your future systems and plans. Whatever you buy in the future, it will be right at home with the investment you have already made.
<DD>Panorama means step-by-step implementation. Everything you buy today is prepared for future expansion or upgrading. <BR>
And just like Panorama, your investments are here to stay.</td>

