<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>TELESCOPE Sipping</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="headabba.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=5><TR>
<TD><FONT SIZE=5><B>TELESCOPE Sipping</B></FONT></TD>
</TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="telesipp.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0><TR>
<TD WIDTH=478>
Fuel leak detection of irradiated nuclear fuel is carried out to secure a safe and economic operation of the fuel, and to prevent high radioactivity levels in the nuclear power station.
<P>
ABB Atom performs complete sipping programs including planning, measurement and evaluations. The new, safe and accurate leak detection method is TELESCOPE Sipping.
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>References</FONT>
<BR>
TELESCOPE Sipping has been successfully performed in BWRs and PWRs in Sweden, Finland, Germany and U.S.A.
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>Further information</FONT>
<BR>
For further information, please contact the Department of Marketing and Sales,<BR>
Field Services Division
phone +46 (0)21 34 70 00</TD>
</TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="linerbow.gif"></CENTER>
