<HEAD>
<TITLE>ABB Network Partners - the Company 3</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY  BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#FF0A11" VLINK="#930000">
<IMG ALIGN=Right SRC="logo.gif" WIDTH=116 HEIGHT=55 BORDER=0>

<TABLE CELLSPACING=1 CELLPADDING=0 BORDER=0>
<TR valign=top>
	<TD  height=100 WIDTH=180>
<A HREF="senete.html"><IMG SRC="netbut.JPG" WIDTH=120 HEIGHT=15 border=0></A><p>

</TD>
<TD WIDTH=500 colspan=2>&nbsp;</TD>

<TR VALIGN=TOP>
	<TD WIDTH=140></TD>
<td WIDTH=400 HEIGHT=40 colspan=2></td>

<TR VALIGN=TOP>
		<TD WIDTH=180 valign=top><IMG ALIGN=no SRC="promise.JPG" WIDTH=180 HEIGHT=115 BORDER=0><p>
<I>Our name is<BR>
a Promise  </i></TD>

<td WIDTH=400 COLSPAN=3>

<FONT SIZE=+3>Our name ABB Network Partner AB<BR>
 is a promise. The idea of partnership <BR>
runs through everything we do.</FONT> <P>


We want to work close to our customers in order to jointly define the actual needs of an information and control system. We also assist in specifying the right type of solution. We can analyze various projects and calculate their profitability.<P>

<B>A constant dialogue</B><BR>
Through our worldwide organization we are in a constant dialogue with our customers. We're always close at hand.

<DD>We exchange ideas. We develop products together. We share projects. We try out new perspectives. In other words, we're right in the middle of where things are happening, with our customers. In many countries we've built up a strong organization to solve our customers' needs, deliver turnkey solutions, take care of maintenance and support as well as have an ear to the ground regarding the customers' needs for not only today but tomorrow.

<DD>It's no coincidence. As supplier, in order to offer top functionality, maximum performance and highest quality, we have to listen to what our customers are saying. As an example of this, our quality system is certified according to ISO 9001.<P>

<B>Over 10% to research and development</B><BR>
In our business, things develop fast. In many senses, ABB Network Partner AB is a pure IT-company.

<DD>Within our company, we have the most advanced CAD/CAM tools available. Every engineer is connected to our company wide area network to speed up and secure development work. We even have one of the world's fastest real-time simulator for testing protection relays.

<DD>Our aim is not just to stay abreast of the change, but to lead it. That's why we strive for the best and most well-educated staff by continually developing their competence. In addition, we invest over 10% of our turnover into R&D. And we have access to the rest of the business area's efforts in research. <P>

<B>World class production and project management</B><BR>
Our modern production processes are built with IT in mind. This creates shorter delivery times and on-time deliveries. 

<DD>Experience from deliveries all over the world has led us to an effective and systematic project model. A model which helps us work together with our customers to reach joint delivery goals.<P>

<B>Support after the contract</B><BR>
Our involvement doesn't stop once the order is taken and the delivery made. 
We offer extensive resources for the training of the personnel who will be using our systems and products. Training in the classroom and in the field. Often, the end users will be part of the project team so that they can affect the final result.

<DD>We also provide support when it comes to maintenance, system expansion and of course system upgrades. We assist in the gradual upgrading of older systems to new techniques or functions. Panorama makes it possible to build individual modules thanks to modular thinking. Thus resulting in a life-cycle cost reduction.
<P>
That's why an investment in Panorama is always profitable.
<P>&nbsp;<P></td>


<TR VALIGN=TOP>
	<TD WIDTH=140>
